<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Georg_Friedrich_Grotefend.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Georg_Friedrich_Grotefend" title="Georg Friedrich Grotefend">Georg Friedrich Grotefend</a></div>
</div>
</div>
