<div class="thumbimage" style="height:159px;overflow:hidden"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Edward_Hincks.jpg/132px-Edward_Hincks.jpg" width="132" height="159" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Edward_Hincks.jpg/198px-Edward_Hincks.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Edward_Hincks.jpg/264px-Edward_Hincks.jpg 2x" data-file-width="466" data-file-height="561" /></div>
