<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Relative_pronouns">Relative pronouns</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Akkadian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=29" title="Edit section: Relative pronouns">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
