<p>Akkadian was also a source of borrowing to other languages, above all <a href="/wiki/Sumerian_language" title="Sumerian language">Sumerian</a>. Some examples are: Sumerian <i>da-ri</i> ('lastingly', from Akkadian <i>dƒÅru</i>), Sumerian <i>ra gaba</i> ('riders, messenger', from Akkadian <i>rƒÅkibu</i>).</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Sample_text">Sample text</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Akkadian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=37" title="Edit section: Sample text">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
