<p>Translation: <i>If a man has bought silver or gold, a male or a female slave, an ox, a sheep, or a donkey‚Äîor anything for that matter‚Äîfrom another man or from another man‚Äôs slave without witnesses or contract, or if he accepted something for safekeeping without same, then this man is a thief and hence to be killed.</i></p>
